main event: Observers watched a group of several objects about the size of large birds or small airplanes for nearly 20 minutes.
interesting points: The objects were white, red, and green., The objects appeared to move and maneuver in a somewhat erratic manner., One of the objects appeared to disappear and reappear in a different location., The sighting lasted for nearly 20 minutes., No physical evidence was found.
witness description: military personnel from the Coast Guard
